{
  "stem": "3085.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that point, I wasn't really concerned with what they felt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were just trying to, to survive and to make sure that-- see how much we can take over to, to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because all we got-- I mean, we had a house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had a, a, a, a fairly substantial house before the war and early part of the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when we had to move to that ghetto, we-- all we got was one room.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now, at that point, my father wasn't with us anymore because he had been taken away to what was called a labor brigade or whatever they-- I'm not sure how to translate it.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was like labor service, where all able-bodied men were actually called up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they weren't necessarily on the front, but they were assisting Hungarian Army in the war effort with menial jobs and, and that type of thing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, they weren't fighting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They weren't trusted to fight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But, but they were doing menial jobs for, for the army and the Hungarian forces.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So all the able-bodied men were taken away, including my father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that, of course, eliminated any possibility of resistance, which was, of course, the primary purpose of it is-- I mean, if the men are not there, who's going to rebel?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And who's going to fight?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So at that point, only my mother and the three children-- my sister and my brother and I, four of us-- were in, in-- sort of taken to the ghetto and, and put in one room.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK, we'll pause there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we'll pick up on the next tape.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
